<br>
Go to erudite merchant in East Commons and buy an entire bag of bat wings, then go to the two brother merchants in East Freeport in the Transit Authority next to docks and buy a bag full of fish.  Go to an over and combine 1 bat with and 1 fish...for a fishroll....will get you to 135.  May need to make several trips to refill bags with batwings and fish.  Lots of fails early on but after about 2 hours I went from 1 to 130...<br>
