<br>
Some guildmates of mine decided they would go do this quest and kill the Kromrif Death Squads for experience. This did work a couple times, when only two Death Squads spawned. Sometimes as many as six can spawn, though. Since they are giants they cannot be mezzed or stunned, so they had to root down the extras. They are not immune to magic, but they are highly resistant. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> They can outrun jboots.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->They are also just downright tough, a lot of hitpoints.<br>
<br>
